column3: â€œSmoked with a friend and we both loved Tangerine so much that we went back to buy more the next morning. This is a fun, euphoric, giggly and potent high with energy in the beginning and then deep happy relaxation at the end. We highly recommend this strain!â€

â€œI enjoyed Tangerine but it is definitely a strong sativa-dominant hybrid.
